Hey, this is my one night project "surf_baldrian" :]

every round u start with a knife only, so u have to be fast to get a weapon first. u can get high on top of the map on 2 different platforms ;) there is also a secret what i will net tell you now xD
if u realise that u are in jail- climb up as fast as u can to not get killed :>
(sorry for my bad english)

hope you like it! rate and let me read some feedback, thanks <3
